
The release 2.1 (Punica granatum) of Flora-2 fixes many bugs and adds new
features. This release includes self-contained Windows, Mac, and Linux
installers.

The installer flora2.run is for the users of Linux/Mac/Other Unixes.
The installer flora2.exe is for Windows users.

Details of the changes can be found in the release notes at http://flora.sourceforge.net/release_notes.html
The installation instructions are simple and are available at http://flora.sourceforge.net/installation.html
